      <virtual-method name="fix_symmetry" invoker="fix_symmetry">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libipuz/docs/ipuz-crossword-docs.c"
             line="216">Enforce the board symmetry of the cells in @summetry_coords in the
direction of @symmetry. That is to say, go through each cell in
@symmetry_coords and make sure that the appropriate cell at the
point(s) of symmetry have the same [enum@Ipuz.CellType].

In addition, subclasses of [class@Ipuz.Crossword] may do further
fixups.</doc>
        <source-position filename="libipuz/ipuz-crossword.h" line="62"/>
        <return-value transfer-ownership="none">
